  "content": "          <div style=\"font-size: 18px; color: var(--text-secondary); margin-top: 4px;\">Conversations vanish after each session. But how do you store them without polluting the knowledge base?</div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"insight-box\">\n    <p>These are directions, not tasks. Jumping straight to code from here means rewriting things three times. The gap between \"vague idea\" and \"actionable issue board\" is where the real work happens.</p>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"flex-grow\"></div>\n  <div class=\"author-tag\">Lim Chun Zhe</div>\n  <div class=\"slide-number\">02 / 09</div>\n</div>\n\n<!-- SLIDE 3: LAYER 1 OVERVIEW -->\n<div class=\"slide\">\n  <div class=\"slide-label\" style=\"color: var(--accent-cyan);\">Layer 1: The Creative Phase</div>\n  <div class=\"slide-title\" style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;\">\n    Explore. Design.<br>\n    <span class=\"highlight-cyan\">Structure.</span>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"slide-subtitle\" style=\"font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 28px;\">\n    This is where I learn. Trade-offs, judgment calls, and decisions that Claude can't make alone.\n  </div>",
